{"tid":1823704,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"葵涌兩男女餐廳交收狗肉 涉管有狗隻屠體被捕","createTime":"2020-01-14T02:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T02:45:55.000Z","uid":214261,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dde2c308b5f1c02081a78046ca1dd65b87615c73","tid":1823704,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:12:47.000Z","msg":"葵涌兩男女餐廳交收狗肉 涉管有狗隻屠體被捕<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n武漢肺炎來勢洶洶，病毒疑經野味散播，懷疑源頭的武漢華南海鮮批發市場日前起休市。香港至今已出現68宗相關病人個案，但有港人仍未知驚，懷疑在內地購買狗肉後偷運返港，今日在葵涌交收時被市民舉報，遭警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n今早10時許，警方接獲一名女子報案，指葵涌葵盛東邨商場一餐廳內，有兩名男女藏有一袋狗肉。警員到場後，經初步調查，撿獲一袋約重850克的懷疑狗肉，並拘捕一名77歲姓陳老翁及76歲姓黃老婦，涉嫌管有狗隻屠體。消息稱，黃婦早前在內地購買狗肉，其後偷運回港，在上址與陳翁交收。<br />\n<br />\n內地部份地區狗肉是餐桌上的美味佳餚，但在香港食狗屬犯法。根據香港法例第167章第3條《貓狗規例》，任何人不得屠宰任何貓狗以作食物之用，不論其是否供人食用，以及不得售賣或使用或允許他人售賣或使用狗肉及貓肉作食物；另外，任何人被發現管有任何貓狗屠體或該等屠體任何部份，且其情況合理地令人相信該貓狗隻是在本條的規定被觸犯的情況下，正在或經已被屠宰或售賣或使用作食物，亦屬違法。違者可處罰款5,000元及監禁6個月。 <br />\n<br />\n------------<br />\n有乜理由香港仲未有死亡個案<br />\n梗係要運啲狗肉落嚟<br />\n一齊共享榮耀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26699ba587ad953cc981e45d3258afd4ba32770f","tid":1823704,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報報導<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200113/60481535?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200113%2F60481535%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=5a5105da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200113%2F60481535%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_applecitycrime%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e77fe83f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20200113/60481535?utm_campaign=hkad_social_applecitycrime&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"a6fbbee8aa6a1916825f4c547fb0b370ac393c58","tid":1823704,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"依個時勢切勿跟車太貼"},{"pid":"06d7a73fa733ff6f8c154c8dc26feb4a9dfbbfa2","tid":1823704,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6fbbee8aa6a1916825f4c547fb0b370ac393c58","tid":1823704,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:17:06.000Z","msg":"依個時勢切勿跟車太貼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"咩意思？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通係假新聞？"},{"pid":"5c03200aa0c381cd0b0dedb829abe150775c9f4c","tid":1823704,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:36:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4aa7e0b2e297293d733c3129d8dde8465d8df99","tid":1823704,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:36:51.000Z","msg":"華夏文化被拉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d55855fa6098f5961023388d79b86668f2ed429","tid":1823704,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:44:52.000Z","msg":"吃狗肉，是你身為中國人天生的權利。香港禁食狗肉，是一條親英反中的惡法，你是中國人，你要公民抗命。<br />\n我說：如果有人投訴，你就駁斥：吃狗肉是中國文化，抓人，你可以笑嘻嘻，你叫他們「包容」。如果有警察上門，提醒警察：一九六七年，你們是愛國中國人眼中的黃皮狗，你抓我，是想報復，此一歷史仇怨，還是想維護同類呀？<br />\n看見五星旗而流淚，喜食狗肉，或至少看見屠狗而無動於衷，而不是反過來，我認為，是衡量一個「中國人」的兩大標準。"},{"pid":"d51cc888e6ec2cbd80246d6c407176d59a979d86","tid":1823704,"uid":333470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T02:45:55.000Z","msg":"七張幾都果頭近就咪搞呢啲嘢來害人 積下陰德啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}